Speaker 1: Hello, how are you doing, sir? This is Quinn speaking. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Hello. I'm sorry, what was your name?

Speaker 1: Quinn.

Speaker 2: Is there a Jimmy around there? I was talking to one last week.

Speaker 1: Yeah, there sure is a Jimmy. You sure you want to talk to him?

Speaker 2: Yeah, last week I was talking to him, and he sent me some stuff saying it was going to be different.

Speaker 1: And he sent me the same exact stuff.

Speaker 2: And he sent you the same stuff. Okay, I'm going to get you right over to him. One moment.

Speaker 1: Cool.

Speaker 2: I'm just going to put you in a brief hold, sir. It should probably be like not even a couple seconds. He'll pick up.

Speaker 1: All right, thanks.
